; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日上午，嘉鱼县洲湾抗洪烈士陵园内庄严肃穆，由嘉鱼县委、县政府和空军</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">95025</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">部队联合主办的大型祭扫活动在此举行。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县四大家领导，空军</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">95025</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">部队官兵代表，烈士亲属代表，县人武部、武警、消防官兵代表，县直部门相关负责人，洲湾镇全体机关干部和中小学生代表及社会各界群众近千人在抗洪烈士陵园隆重集会，深切悼念为保护人民的生命财产而英勇献身的抗洪英烈们。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇在仪式上致辞。他说，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1998</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年的那场特大洪水肆虐南嘉大地时，是人民子弟兵不顾个人安危，救民于水深火热之中。为了嘉鱼人民的生命财产安全，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">19</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">名官兵将年轻的生命永远留在了这里，他们用生命谱写了一首人生的赞歌。英魂不朽，浩气长存，抗洪精神永远激励着嘉鱼人民。县委、县政府将带领全县人民，努力实现建设&ldquo;湖北经济强县、长江临港新城&rdquo;的奋斗目标，以告慰英烈在天之灵。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委副书记、县长余珂主持祭扫仪式。县领导李鹏谋、葛婷、熊武华、李新华、朱从钦、魏萍，县人武部部长王俊、县委办主任章斌、县政府办主任周长明参加了祭扫活动。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">空军</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">95025</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">部队政委陈鹏在仪式上发言，表达了对烈士们的深切缅怀之情。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">公祭仪式上，县四大家领导和</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">95025</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">部队领导向烈士纪念墓敬献了花圈和花篮，来自洲湾镇蓝天中学的学生们排成队向烈士墓敬献鲜花，并在墓碑前宣誓：刻苦学习，倍加珍惜来之不易的美好家园。<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0401/20120401044727969.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /></span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体;\\\\\">参加祭扫活动的全体人员默哀三分钟</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0401/20120401044741282.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">学生们向烈士墓献花</span></font></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1450','287','雷明清','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/xiyingshibadazhengchuangxinyeji/2012-04-01/aa1f20da9076fb24f929315d76b6d987.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">31</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日上午，嘉鱼县地税局召开全县地税系统党风廉政建设会暨&ldquo;喜迎十八大、争创新业绩&rdquo;主题实践活动推进会。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会上，该局两名班子成员分别部署了全县地税系统党风廉政建设及&ldquo;喜迎十八大、争创新业绩&rdquo;主题实践活动的相关工作。每人用时不超过</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">分钟；市地税局纪检组长程志平，县纪委副书记、监察局长吕太平在会上作简短讲话，均不超过</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">分钟；最后，县地税局局长余显忠结合自身工作实践的即席讲话言简意赅，仅用时</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">28</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">分钟，整个会议在</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">小时内圆满结束。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times