yle=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">辆公车参与清明祭扫，分别属于县烟草局、县药监局、县质监局。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">13</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">日，嘉鱼县治庸问责大会上，有关部门播出专题片曝光暗访发现的问题。台下的一些相关单位负责人，有的涨红了脸，有的低下了头。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据当日通报：县发改局等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">家单位公务员被发现迟到；县统计局、商务局、行政服务中心</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">名工作人员，在工作时间上网玩游戏、聊天、看视频；元月以来，县工会等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">13</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">家单位负责人未经请假缺席会议，甚至请人顶替参会，其中县银监局就有</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">次。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">县联通公司、县中华联合保险公司、县人寿保险公司，因在&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动中挖塘措施、资金不到位，也被通报批评。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">县纪委根据治庸办提供的线索，近期查办了</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">起党员干部违纪违法案件。县房管局房屋安全鉴定所副所长熊经权，在县&ldquo;两违&rdquo;指挥部暂停危房鉴定期间，采取前推鉴定时间、提高鉴定等级等手段，为请托人出具房屋安全鉴定报告。县纪委给予其留党察看一年的处分，县住建局免除其职务。负有失察责任的县房管局副局长被诫勉谈话。&ldquo;庸懒散软问题，远不止这些。我们要真治、敢治、重治、大治，营造干事业的良好环境，推进建设经济强县。&rdquo;县委书记熊征宇斩钉截铁。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据介绍，开展治庸问责以来，该县已督办整改各类问题</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">150</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">余个，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">149</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">人被问责。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1476','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-14/2c5867c1a111bfae742b10370414d215.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">图为会议现场</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" month=\\\\\"4\\\\\" day=\\\\\"13\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>日</st1:chsdate>，嘉鱼县召开&ldquo;建设湖北经济强县&rdquo;第一次座谈会暨项目建设、治庸问责推进会。会议主要任务贯彻落实全省县域经济工作会议精神，动员全县上下要掀起新一轮思想大解放、作风大转变、项目大建设的热潮，为加快推进湖北经济强县、长江临港新城建设步伐凝神聚力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇说，近期，县委组织考察团赴湖南、江西、福建、陕西等地进行了考察学习，此次考察对我县进一步解放思想、开拓视野，增强发展的紧迫感非常有意义。通过此次外出考察学习，大家要深刻认识到，在当前及今后一段时期的工作中，解放思想、项目建设、优化环境、转变作风的重要性。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇强调，解放思想要常抓不懈。当今社会环境、要求、现状都在不断变化，要求我们的思想观念也要随之转变。解放思想反映一个地方干部的精神状态，体现一个地方的发展速度。因此，我县必须敢于直面差距，敢于以舍求得，敢于逆向思维，敢于&ldquo;攀大求洋&rdquo;，敢于破解难题，敢于重奖重罚，大手笔、大气魄地进行招商引资，营造你追我赶的良好发展氛围。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇指出，项目建设要大干快上，加快构建大园区平台，加大园区建设资金投入，进一步创新园区基础设施建设投入模式，为后期项目落户打下良好基础；要着力强化项目建设中的机制保障，落实县级领导联点责任制，项目进度考评责任制，项目进度督办责任制，力争做到一个项目一个责任领导一个责任单位，重点项目建设进度进行每月一通报、每季度一督查，年终进行考核考评。他强调，全县各级各部门要开展好&ldquo;百日专班大招商、百日环境大整治、百日项目大会战&rdquo;活动，促进各项目加快建设，尽快投产。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇要求，优化环境要全面推进，着力打造高效廉洁的政务环境，包容开放的人文环境，宜居宜业的城市环境，快速便捷的物流环境，诚实守信的信用环境，全面推进软硬环境建设，打造投资&ldquo;高地&rdquo;。他强调，转变作风要一抓到底，结合治庸问责活动，进一步增强领导带头的引导力，推进工作的意志力，狠抓落实的执行力，严明纪律的约束力，掀起新一轮干部作风大转变热潮。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委副书记、县长余珂就考察学习情况作了全面总结，他说，此次参观考察的几个县市区，给大家留下的印象是越先进发达的地区，发展的气场越大，发展的气魄越大。结合我县实际，嘉鱼要切实做到大目标引领、大园区承载、大项目支撑、大手笔运筹、大力度推进，以矢志不移的决心，深入推进思想解放；以拼命三郎的精神，全力推进项目建设，围绕政策导向、资源开发、区域特色千方百计引项目；以刮骨疗伤的勇气，强力推进治庸问责，切实改进工作作风，改革办事流程，改善投资环境，真正营造全社会亲商、安商、富商的良好氛围，以优质的服务，良好的作风为跨越式发展提供持续动力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委副书记李国光主持会议，李鹏谋、葛婷、熊武华、李新华、袁秋明、朱从钦、刘合权、房健等县四大家领导出席会议。县直各单位主要负责人及班子成员，各镇党委书记、镇长、副书记，规模企业负责人代表等参加会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议下发了《关于加强推进全县重点项目建设实施办法》、《关于加强干部作风建设优化发展环境的意见》等<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>个相关文件。与会人员观看了重点项目建设进度通报和治庸问责中查处案件及明察暗访情况通报短片。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县经济开发区、县国土局、鱼岳镇、潘家湾镇负责人在会上作了典型发言；县文体新局、县房管局负责人在会上作了治庸问责工作表态发言。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 8.15pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 8.15pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 8.15pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 8.15pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1478','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-16/45d08ff6038322aaa3d86ae660e8a7d0.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">在城区三环线项目建设现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-16/7b3ccbfc80d0ca23391858d65219eb7d.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">在洁丽雅二期建设现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"15\\\\\" month=\\\\\"4\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>日下午</st1:chsdate>，县委书记熊征宇，县委副书记、县长余珂对我县重点项目建设推进情况进行检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">熊征宇一行先后来到城区三环线项目、大连成达加工项目、洁丽雅纺织嘉鱼产业基地二期项目、京珠连接线改建拓宽项目现场，实地了解相关项目的建设进展，并听取各项目负责人的情况介绍，详细了解每一项目的进展、存在的问题及下一步工作计划。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">在各项目建设现场，运输车辆来回穿梭，各负责领导和责任单位人员对照图纸认真指挥，一派火热景象。熊征宇要求，各重点项目建设单位要在保证施工质量和安全的前提下，加快建设进度，确保项目能够按照既定时序推进。相关部门要明确目标责任，强化协调服务，及时帮助解决项目在推进过程中遇到的问题，全力促进项目快建设、早竣工、速达效。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据了解，为推进重点项目加快建设，我县对当前全县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">56</span>个重点项目确定了责任领导、第一责任单位、责任单位，并确定了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年度建设内容，督促各项目保证建设质量和加快建设进度。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">目前，城区三环线建设、大连成达、洁丽雅二期、京珠连接线改建项目均在进行土地平整。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年度，城区三环线项目将完成路基工程，预计明年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>月份可全部完工；大连成达加工项目厂房即将开始动工建设；洁丽雅纺织二期项目已完成年产<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>万吨特种纱生产线、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.5</span>万吨毛巾生产线厂房和办公楼主体建筑；京珠连接线改建拓宽项目即将完成征地、拆迁、花坛绿化和人行道、路灯、过路涵管安装等工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">县领导李国光、熊武华、谢望松、朱从钦、李德炳、许隆高、雷家兴，及各项目责任单位负责人参加检查。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1479','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-16/b5b24a9ee9b0ec1dd68347a4376b3330.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">座谈会现场<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">16</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，通山县委副书记张明新，县委常委、政法委书记镇卫军，副县长阮仕林一行赴嘉鱼县就&ldquo;两违&rdquo;整治工作进行参观考察。县领导熊征宇、李国光、朱从钦陪同考察。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">通山考察组一行实地参观了我县工业园拆违点，观看了嘉鱼&ldquo;两违&rdquo;整治纪录片，并听取了我县&ldquo;两违&rdquo;整治工作情况介绍。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">随后召开的座谈会上，县委书记熊征宇说，随着城市建设的推进，违法违规建设的危害性愈发显现，不仅扰乱了城市总体规划的实施，对城市建设、管理和经营都有极大的负面影响，同时也损害了广大群众的利益。他强调，正是认识到&ldquo;两违&rdquo;的危害性，嘉鱼县委、县政府决心下猛药割除城市&ldquo;毒瘤&rdquo;，主要领导亲自部署，靠前指挥，各相关部门积极行动，始终保持了高压态势。目前，全县&ldquo;两违&rdquo;建设得到有效遏制，&ldquo;两违&rdquo;整治工作取得了阶段性成果。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">通山县委副书记张明新说，通过参观现场和听取情况介绍，深刻感受到了嘉鱼在&ldquo;两违&rdquo;整治工作上的决心和力度，也看到了嘉鱼城市管理所取得的成果。这次来嘉鱼考察，就是为了学习嘉鱼在城市建设和管理、拆违控违工作中取得的先进经验，以更好地推动通山的&ldquo;两违&rdquo;整治工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，今年以来，我县组织集中拆违三次，拆违面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余平方米。目前我县&ldquo;两违&rdquo;建设得到有效遏制，社会反响良好。下一步，我县将按照疏堵结合的原则，进一步加大&ldquo;两违&rdquo;整治政策宣传力度，落实包保责任，认真做好违建户及广大群众的思想工作，巩固&ldquo;两违&rdquo;整治成果，健全防违控违长效机制。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1480','284','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">继全县召开项目建设、治庸问责工作推进会后，各镇、各部门迅速行动，召开主题会议，传达贯彻全县会议精神，全面掀起思想大解放、作风大转变、项目大建设热潮。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县农业局组织全体干部学习了《治庸问责通报》以及县委、县政府关于进一步重申相关规定和纪律的通知，并要求将文件精神传达给农业系统每一位干部职工。该局规定严格实行干部档案日报制，每日上下班要实事求是的填写好考勤档案；严格实行日常工作例会制，每周一召开机关日常工作例会，对每周工作进行部署安排，落实到人；严格实行工作进展月报制，每月对安排工作完成情况进行内部通报，以提高工作效率。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县司法局在全县大会结束后，第一时间组织全体干部一同学习县治庸问责工作文件，传达全县会议精神。要求要明确目标，突出重点，狠抓落实，着力从思想上、作风上、行动上、制度上下大力整治目前干部队伍中存在的&ldquo;庸懒散软恶&rdquo;现象，要以空前的紧迫感和危机感来对待治庸问责工作。会议对局治庸检查小组查找出来的问题进行了严厉的批评及整改，并对会议纪律、上下班签到、请假流程、工作与学习等方面作了具体规定。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p