char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">为了组织实施国家免费孕前优生健康检查项目试点工作，大力推进优生促进工程，积极探索建立&ldquo;政府主导、部门合作、专家支撑、群众参与&rdquo;的出生缺陷一级预防工作机制，保证试点工作的顺利实施，特制定本方案。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 黑体\\\\\">一、指导思想<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">以科学发展观为指导，坚持以人为本，依托人口和计划生育服务网络优势，面向社会、面向家庭、面向计划怀孕农村夫妇，开展免费孕前优生健康检查，从源头抓起，将出生缺陷预防关口前移，提高计划怀孕农村夫妇健康水平，有效降低出生缺陷发生风险，促进出生人口素质提高。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 黑体\\\\\">二、工作原则<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（一）积极宣传引导。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">开展免费孕前优生健康检查工作试点，是在实施优生促进工程中采取的一项重要措施，是一项为群众办实事办好事的民心工程，各地各有关部门要广泛做好宣传发动工作，扩大群众知晓面，引导目标人群积极参与。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（二）坚持知情自愿。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">按照公开、知情、自愿的原则，客观告知受检者所检查项目的内容、必要性和检查结果、技术水平的局限性等，充分尊重受检者的选择权利，引导计划怀孕农村夫妇参加免费孕前优生健康检查。检查前签署知情选择同意书。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（三）坚持依法服务</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">参与试点的技术服务单位和技术服务人员，必须具备与所开展的检查项目相符合的合法执业资质，采购合法的药品（试剂）、检查设备等，使用标准技术，按照专项技术操作规范的要求，量力而行开展服务，必要时及时转诊。禁止超范围服务。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（四）坚持科学指导</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">预防出生缺陷是一项科学性很强的工作，要充分发挥专家在制定工作方案、人员培训、专业指导、效果评价等方面的作用，及时解决试点工作中遇到的技术性疑难问题。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（五）坚持方便群众</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">各地根据实际，认真组织策划、细化、优化各工作环节的服务内容和方法，尽可能为受检者提供方便快捷的服务。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（六）坚持保密原则。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">为保护和尊重计划怀孕农村夫妇的权益，对他们的基本信息、孕前优生健康检查内容及结果、出生缺陷风险评估结果及干预措施、建议等必须予以保密。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 黑体\\\\\">三、工作目标<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">通过试点，积极探索适合我县免费孕前优生健康检查工作模式，提高服务机构开展出生缺陷一级预防的能力，逐步构建起政府保障有力、预防服务到位、目标人群广泛参与的出生缺陷一级预防服务体系。具体目标是：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（一）增强计划怀孕农村夫妇预防出生缺陷的风险意识和防御能力。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">全县计划怀孕夫妇优生科学知识知晓率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80%</span>；接受孕前优生健康检查的计划怀孕夫妇的知识知晓率达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>；已生育病残儿的夫妇再生育优生指导服务率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（二）改善计划怀孕农村夫妇健康情况</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">对计划怀孕夫妇检出患生殖健康疾病，存在影响优生因素者给予力所能及的治疗或提出转诊建议，帮助及时转诊率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">95%</span>。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（三）完善出生缺陷一级预防工作机制。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">总结孕前优生健康检查试点工作经验，为完善我县出生缺陷一级预防服务体系建设提供借鉴，促进全县出生缺陷一级预防服务能力进一步提高。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 黑体\\\\\">四、主要工作内容<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（一）确定试点工作目标人群</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">目标人群为全县各类符合生育政策、计划怀孕的农村夫妇，包括流动人口计划怀孕夫妇。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（二）确定孕前优生健康检查人员数量</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">根据国家、省人口计生部门的要求，对政策内计划怀孕的一孩、二孩夫妇确定为我县首批&ldquo;孕前优生健康检查&rdquo;对象，要求孕前优生健康检查比例达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">70%</span>。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（三）明确孕前优生健康检查基本服务内容</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">向计划怀孕夫妇提供安全、规范、符合服务对象个性需求的全程服务，包括优生健康教育、病史询问、体格检查、临床实验室检查、影像学检查、风险评估、咨询指导、早孕及妊娠结局追踪随访等<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">19</span>个项目。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">(</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">四<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">)</span>认真总结试点经验</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">认真收集、汇总、统计、分析试点工作的数据、资料，总结孕前优生健康检查服务的工作经验，为完善全县出生缺陷一级预防体系，提高服务质量提供对策、建议和经验。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 黑体\\\\\">五、试点工作程序<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">试点工作于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月启动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（一）准备阶段</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月。成立领导小组，制定国家免费孕前优生健康检查项目试点工作方案。为确保全县优生促进工程有序开展，县人民政府成立嘉鱼县优生促进工程项目实施领导小组，由副县长魏萍任组长，县人民政府办公室副主任罗瑛、县人口计生局局长杜晓龙任副组长，县财政局张晓萍、县人口计生局张京发、县卫生局张昌录、县民政局章桂兰、县妇联罗婷任成员。领导小组负责优生促进工程项目实施的组织领导和检查督办。领导小组下设办公室，办公室设在县人口计生局，张京发兼任办公室主任。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">县计生服务站要严格按照技术标准，建立规范的优生健康检查监测室，配备相应设备；制定详细的实施方案，成立优生促进工程项目专家组，建立免费孕前优生健康检查相应制度；挑选有检验资质、有经验的服务人员从事具体检查工作。各镇计生服务中心积极配合开展试点工作。各级计生干部积极开展宣传动员工作，培训各级技术骨干。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（二）实施阶段</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">2012</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4-12</span>月。制订国家免费孕前优生健康检查项目试点工作方案，召开全县免费孕前优生健康检查项目试点启动会。广泛宣传动员群众，开展健康教育，进行健康检查，提供风险评估，为一般人群或高危人群进行有针对性的优生指导，并根据目标人群的需求改进服务工作。建立《国家免费孕前优生健康检查项目技术服务家庭档案》，按照孕前优生健康检查基本项目内容，指导计划怀孕夫妇知情同意、科学选择相应的检查项目；在开展优生相关实验室检查时，选择经食品药品监督管理部门批准的检查设备和检测试剂，按照标准程序，严格规范操作。要按照《国家免费孕前优生健康检查项目技术服务规范（试行）》要求，科学规范开展工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（三）评估阶段</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">2013</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>月。收集、汇总、统计、分析国家免费孕前优生健康检查项目试点工作经验，由县人口计生局组织评估；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">31</span>日前，由县人口计生局将试点工作总结和评估报告报送省、市人口计生委。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 黑体\\\\\">六、工作要求<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（一）加强组织领导</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">各镇要高度重视试点工作，明确专人负责国家免费孕前优生健康检查项目试点工作的组织、实施，建立国家免费孕前优生健康检查知情选择同意制度。县计划生育服务站承担孕前优生健康检查的技术服务和有关资料的收集、统计、分析工作。镇计生办和计生服务中心积极配合，做好孕前优生健康检查的宣传、动员、组织等工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（二）加强质量控制</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">孕前优生健康检查工作科学技术性强，各地各有关部门要选配综合素质好、有责任心、服务能力强的人员从事此项工作，严格按照服务规范和流程开展工作，以确保孕前优生健康检查服务质量，尽最大可能降低服务风险。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（三）保证工作经费</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">。根据我县近<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>年出生新生儿数量和经费情况，测算县级经费需投入的配套资金数额，确保试点工作所需的经费投入。要加强经费使用的管理和监督，确保免费孕前优生健康检查试点工作任务圆满完成，切实让群众受益。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\\\\\">（四）做好宣传发动</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\">。各地各部门要加大对计划怀孕夫妇和育龄群众进行免费孕前优生健康检查工作宣传力度，提高计划怀孕夫妇对进行孕前优生健康检查重要性、必要性的认识，增强其积极参与和接受孕前优生健康检查的自觉性和主动性。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");

